Compare {{cog|cy|gwelw||pale}}, {{cog|la|helvus||dull yellow}}, {{cog|ga|geal||white, bright}}, {{cog|lt|Å¾alias||green}}, {{cog|grc|Ï‡Î»Ï‰ÏÏŒÏ‚||light green}}, {{cog|fa|Ø²Ø±Ø¯|tr=zard||yellow}}, {{cog|sa|à¤¹à¤°à¤¿||greenish-yellow}}. Cognate with {{cog|de|gelb||yellow}}, {{cog|nl|geel||yellow}}.
The verb is from {{inh|en|ang|Ä¡eolwian}}, from the adjective.
